QuestData.Title: Secure Seabrush
QuestData.Description: The Alliance has spies in this area? Tenebrous Cavern is nearby, and inside lies the Horde's new submarine, the Verne! The Alliance must not be allowed anywhere nearby!$b$bSomeone in the cavern will want to hear of this incursion... after you finish slaying some more of these scheming Alliance spies.
